asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

description: A rappin rabbit with humble roots as deep as the underground in Lord of the Flufs, based in Fluffiton, this head turning poppin rapstar will have you bopping your heads and tails to his incredible FLUF beats with a fresh flavour that might remind you of Scribe or Savage mixed with Justin Timberlake or Jamiraquai. Now you might just think thats just fancy transalliteration, but this rapper can drop his words faster than you can eat a carrot. Rapeti is cousin of Kurt Rapeti Cobain and you can definitely feel the genetics come through. Wait until you see them playing together!  High energy and out of this planet, this s p a c e jammer will have you bopping and hopping off your carrots especially when he drops his techy beats during the zero gravity s p a c e concerts.  This legend will pick you up when youre feeling down, take you higher, and leave you breathless.  As high as this rabbit flies entertaining in the galaxy he still has time for keeping it real with FLUFs, APES, PUNKS and all other meta verse inhabitants that can keep it cool, spreading love, equality, knowledge and spirit as he connects with his lyrics. His favourite food is mooncrust pizza flexitarian flavour of course to reduce his carbon footprint on the galaxy.  Send him some mooncrust pizza as a donation and he might even write some special lyrics for you! Oma Rapeti, Oma, Oma, Oma!!

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: FLUF The Magic Dragon
description:
Coming from a world in which he felt rejected, FLUF The Magic dragon was born under the name Jesser Wormling and made a life of his own. He took the risk of leaving his herd early on to discover a burrow of like-minded FLUFs. 

His life has been a series of adventures, traveling distant lands and evolving along the way. It did not take long until Jesser discovered a land in the warm south within which he discovered a society of unattached and unique FLUFs who shared nothing in common other than their love for EDM. Here, every FLUF was unique and respected, and it did not take long until Jesser discovered his true purpose - to return to the world he came from and spread the word. 

To do this, he shifted his appearance and began creating music - his playlists were so enchanting that he inspired a trance-like state amongst other FLUFs known as the "Dragon State." FLUFs in this state would reproduce at faster rates, develop new exciting projects, and were less likely to come into combat with one than another. The Dragon State was such a powerful tool to create a peaceful FLUF world that Jesser was unanimously awarded the title "FLUF The Magic Dragon" to represent all FLUF that have experienced this State of being. 

Jesser now moves across the Metaverse, playing his music and inspiring new, untouched Herds of FLUF to join the spiritual revolution and live a life of Unison and peace. His Adventures have been kept in countless separate Lores that are maintained and collected under the name "The Dragon Chronicles."
